Package: raiden
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: IceBerg-coder <9084minm@psba.edu.sg>
Description: Blazingly fast parallel downloader for the modern terminal.
 Raiden (rdn) gets your files in a flash using optimized goroutines.
 It features smart segmenting, parallel downloading, and a low footprint.
